title: The Dynamic Duo(s)
description: Katie and Ashley continue the bracket crazy month wackadoo with the final word on the best dynamic duo of all time - and with Bert and Ernie, Key and Peele, and Jordan and Pippen involved, the competition is stiff (13:40). There's also a Very Cavallari Update (50:18) and a Whiskey Cavalier Update (8:55) and a very important Sports? Voting opportunity (1:35:50).
